~I'm looking at how to resolve these merge conflicts and having a tough time figuring out how to add my changes in with the changes introduced in https://github.com/containers/podman/pull/8752. I'm struggling to understand the generated go code and how to cleanly use the new features and types. I was able to get my changes to compile but had very little success otherwise. I don't want to throw out the changes but at the moment I'm not sure if they are still usable. I'm open to suggestions on how to move forward with this feature.~

I think I've had enough time to think this through. I'll keep working on it and try to get something pushed this week... time permitting.

